   JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your-refresh-secret-key-here
   JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=30d<% } %>
   ```

3. **Database setup:**
<% if (orm === 'prisma') { %>
   ```bash
   # Generate Prisma client
   npm run db:generate
   
   # Run migrations
   npm run db:migrate
   
   # Seed database (optional)
